      • SuggestionResult

        public SuggestionResult(HashMap<FieldDescriptor,TermFacetResult<?>> suggestions,
                        String spellcheck,
                        long queryTime,

        Create a new instance of SuggestionResult.
        Parameters:
        suggestions - a map of document fields as keys and suggestions plus count of documents by suggestion as values.
        factory - document factory configured with a document schema.
        spellcheck - String value of the spell check suggestion if existing.
        queryTime - the time the query took in the backend.
        factory - the DocumentFactory used for mapping the results.
